sub_title: Recruiter Chemistry & Life Sciences at CheckMark Labrecruitment
summary:
During my study, I developed a broad interest in biotechnology related topics and fundamental research. However, I have always felt the need to connect with other people and further develop my people skills. My need for social contact led me to CheckMark Labrecruitment. 

As a Recruiter in Chemistry & Life Sciences at CheckMark, my goal is to connect companies to their future employees. For 27 years now CheckMark Labrecruitment is a leading recruitment organization in the Chemistry & Life Sciences industry. We successfully recruit people with an educational level at MLO, HLO, WO or PhD level, from a position as a Technician up to Scientist/Management level with a background in Life Sciences, Chemistry, Food Technology, (Bio) Engineering, Pharmaceuticals, etc. 

Are you looking for a job in Pharma, Biotech or Chemistry? Let's connect!
